{"tid":2374972,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好耐冇試過真心笑過","createTime":"2021-01-21T15:52:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T23:56:59.000Z","uid":77737,"like":84,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"f211171237e698af7f36329722bb8ee98e13fba0","tid":2374972,"uid":77737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T15:52:47.000Z","msg":"自從19年之後好似冇乜好事發生<br />\n衰嘢就日日上演<br />\n返工就越嚟越辛苦<br />\n可能負能量太勁 朋友越嚟越少<br />\n以前會令自己開心嘅嘢都唔再會開心<br />\n就算笑 個心都噏住噏住<br />\n已經想盡辦法谷返起個人<br />\n做運動 睇書 見輔導<br />\n都好似冇咩進展<br />\n做人真係好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲都係咁？"},{"pid":"ec7bf55b79813937be5f6768199d02d76209c0b0","tid":2374972,"uid":199162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T15:53:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46429ea45f3c15ad6b7ada76d43736a56870f6f7","tid":2374972,"uid":77737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec7bf55b79813937be5f6768199d02d76209c0b0","tid":2374972,"uid":199162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T15:53:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T15:55:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e5b6d784827ff02e95c20328fa06b37456d0d0b","tid":2374972,"uid":311128,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T15:56:24.000Z","msg":"今日有啲唔開心，聽歌，睇咗好多集綜藝，笑得好開心，而家一唔睇又開始諗呢樣諗嗰樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20cbddc9b14a062367db59f67358611c83c66328","tid":2374972,"uid":60136,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T15:58:04.000Z","msg":"面朝大海 春暖花開"},{"pid":"85fef274dfce6a219aeb9156fdb953ac12a28a0a","tid":2374972,"uid":77737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e5b6d784827ff02e95c20328fa06b37456d0d0b","tid":2374972,"uid":311128,"like":7,"dislike